  "layoutDesc": {
    "layout": {
      "p": "The inscription occupies the large field between the two columns; the upper part of the inscribed field also contains an engraved laurel-wreath, with the text of the initial lines arranged in and around the wreath (the precise arrangement differs slightly between the two copies). There are clear traces of a previous inscription underlying the existing text, and likewise most of the inscribed face shows the traces of having been beaten smooth prior to re-use.",
